              <h1>Borrowing Related Products</h1>
<div>Borrowing is an act of taking money and paying it back over a period of time.In meeting financial,goals in case the savings is inadequate.Borrowing provides the flexibility of preparing in small installments over time called equated monthly installment (EMI).</div></P>
<div><b>List of document required to get personal loans:</b>
<ul>
<li>Proof of Identity:- passport,/ driving licence,/ voter ID,/ pancard (anyone)</li>
<li>Proof of Residence:- leave and licence agreement/ utility bill/passport(any one)</li>
<li>Latest 3 months bank statement (where salary or income is credited)</li>
<li>Salary slip for last 3 months</li>
<li>Two passport size photographs</li>
<li>Collateral proof</li>
</ul>
<div><p><b>Collateral</b> is a property that a borrower offers as a way for a lender to secure a loan.If the borrower stops making the promised loan payments the lender can seize the collateral,
Lenders claim to borrowers Collateral is called a lien.</p></div>
